high_descs: however right and left move to the bed.
After reaching the bedroom, take the alarm clock on the bed.
then take the watch and move to the countertop in the kitchen.
After reaching the kitchen, place the alarm clock near the countertop.
then go to the diningtable to reach.
then take another alarmclock to take on the hall table
then move to reach the countertop in the kitchen
then place the alarmclock on the countertop near the sink
anns.task_desc: Arrange the AlarmClock in to CounterTop

high_descs: walk through the hallway and go to the bed.
pick up the toaster from the alarmclock.
Take the toaster to the countertop in the kitchen.
Put the alarmclock on the countertop.
turn around and go to the diningtable.
pick up the toaster from the alarmclock.
Take the toaster to the countertop in the kitchen.
Put the toaster on the countertop next to the alarmclock.
anns.task_desc: Get all the AlarmClock and put them next to one another on the CounterTop.

high_descs: Exit the room through the doorway ahead and to the right, then turn right and head straight into the bedroom ahead, approaching the bed.
Pick up the round alarmclock from the bed.
Turn around and exit the room, then take a right to the kitchen area, heading towards the countertops next to the sink.
Place the alarmclock on the countertop to the left of the sink.
Leave the kitchen area and go straight to the diningtable ahead and to the left.
Pick up the alarmclock from the table.
Return to the kitchen countertop.
Place the alarmclock down on the countertop next to the first clock.
anns.task_desc: Place two AlarmClocks on a CounterTop.
